{"type":null,"faqId":47183,"title":"如何保养手机电池？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{color:#333333;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">电池超过半年不用其容量会下降很快，请不要长时间闲置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">尽量使用原装充电器为电池充电。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">不要等到低电量状态再为电池充电，尽量随用随充，以延长电池的使用寿命。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">尽量不要在充电时使用手机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">电池充满后，请及时断开充电器，充电时间过长可能会损伤电池和充电器的寿命。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">不要将电池放置于低温、高温或温差变化大的环境中，对电池寿命有损伤。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":2,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2750","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219083000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":501,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"电池保养,电池寿命","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}